<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
.container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
.header { border-bottom: 2px solid #2e7d32; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.title { color: #2e7d32; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
.info-box { background: #f1f8f2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
.footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 12px; }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header"><div class="title">SurgicalHub — Décompte de prestations</div></div>

  <p>Bonjour <strong>{{ statement.instrumentistNameSnapshot }}</strong>,</p>
  <p>Veuillez trouver ci-joint votre décompte de prestations pour la période <strong>{{ statement.periodMonth|string_pad(2, '0', 'left') }}/{{ statement.periodYear }}</strong>.</p>

  <div class="info-box">
    <strong>Période :</strong> {{ statement.periodMonth|string_pad(2, '0', 'left') }}/{{ statement.periodYear }}<br>
    <strong>Montant total :</strong> {{ statement.totalAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €<br>
    <strong>Lignes :</strong> {{ statement.lines|length }}
  </div>

  <p>Ce document est joint à cet email au format PDF.</p>

  <div class="footer">SurgicalHub — document confidentiel</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
